<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Happy Birthday Ugiary ❤️</title>

<style>
body {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
    font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    color: #fff;
}

.card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 25px;
}

.btn {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    background: #ff4d6d;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

img.main-photo {
    margin-top: 20px;
    width: 260px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    display: none;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
}

.bubu {
    width: 120px;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: -150px;
    animation: naik 4s infinite;
}

.bubu2 {
    right: 10%;
    animation-delay: 2s;
}

.bubu1 {
    left: 10%;
}

@keyframes naik {
    0% {bottom:-150px;}
    50% {bottom:50px;}
    100% {bottom:-150px;}
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {opacity:0; transform:scale(0.8);}
    to {opacity:1; transform:scale(1);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- 🎶 MUSIK LUCU HAPPY BIRTHDAY -->
<audio autoplay loop>
<source src="https://www.bensound.com/bensound-music/bensound-happyrock.mp3">
</audio>

<div class="card">
<h1>🎉 Happy Birthday Ugiary ❤️</h1>

<p>
Selamat ulang tahun yaa sayangku 😚💕<br><br>
Semoga panjang umur & selalu sama aku ya 😝❤️<br><br>
Hari ini kamu resmi naik level jadi makin cantik + makin aku sayang 😭💖
</p>

<button class="btn" onclick="showLove()">Klik Aku 😳</button>

<p id="msg"></p>

<!-- FOTO -->
<img id="photo" class="main-photo"
src="file:///mnt/data/D52C983D-B00A-45A7-8DAA-7348A7FEB9BC.jpeg">

</div>

<!-- 🐻 BUBU DUDU PESTA -->
<img class="bubu bubu1" src="https://media.tenor.com/0AVbKGY_MxMAAAAi/bubu-dudu-sseeyall.gif">
<img class="bubu bubu2" src="https://media.tenor.com/XR9z9qK7X8wAAAAi/bubu-dudu-dance.gif">

<script>
function showLove(){
    document.getElementById("msg").innerHTML =
    "Ini kitaa 😭❤️ pasangan paling gemes sedunia 🥺💖";

    document.getElementById("photo").style.display = "block";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
